  <summary date="2017-03-08T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Repeal Sequestration for Defense Act 

This bill amends the Balanced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985 to eliminate the sequestration for security and defense spending. (Sequestration is a process of automatic, usually across-the-board spending reductions under which budgetary resources are permanently cancelled to enforce specific budget policy goals.)</summary>
